{"id":542228,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/10/【立此存照】《韦氏词典》没有解释taiwan的资格/","date":"2016-10-08T04:28:28Z","modified":"2016-10-08T04:28:28Z","title":"【立此存照】《韦氏词典》没有解释“Taiwan”的资格","content":"<p>【编者注】近日，推特用戶 @taylorwang789 曝光了其所购的全新原版《韦氏词典》中，地名部分被撕掉了两页。推特用户 @redmeteor 认为被撕部分是因为涉及了台湾。她分享了同本词典的“贴条”旧版，同样是地名部分，“Taiwan”一词的解释被白色贴纸完全遮住。</p>\n<p>另有推友 @kaiqiz89 指出，被撕除的两页中或许也有“Tibet”的原因。</p>\n<p>涉台内容在中国大陆一直属于极度敏感的话题。就在上个月，一部 MH370 纪录片曾因出现青天白日满地红旗而<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91mh370%e7%ba%aa%e5%bd%95%e7%89%87%e5%9b%a0%e5%87%ba%e7%8e%b0%e9%9d%92%e5%a4%a9%e7%99%bd%e6%97%a5%e6%bb%a1%e5%9c%b0%e7%ba%a2%e6%97%97%e8%80%8c/\" target=\"_blank\">被视频网站下架</a>。进口原版书籍、杂志等有时也会由于涉及某些敏感话题，在售前被作整页撕除“处理”。</p>\n<blockquote><p>佐拉 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zuola/status/784272521235271680\" target=\"_blank\">@zuola</a>：推特用戶 @taylorwang789 說：「前兩天在上海外文書店買了本英英字典，買回來仔細研究了一下發現被整齊地撕掉了兩頁，看來是不知什麼詞彙違反了當局」另一個用戶 @redmeteor 提供的圖片顯示，字典裡的taiwan词条解释为seat of government被和谐，</p></blockquote>\n<p>‏</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/taylorwang789/status/784221529626189824\" target=\"_blank\">@taylorwang789</a>: @remonwangxt @freedomandlaw 前兩天在上海外文書店買了本英英字典，買之前發現所有的包裝都是拆開的，店員說&#8221;裡面有問題，拆開做了一下處理&#8221;，買回來仔細研究了一下發現被整齊地撕掉了兩頁，看來是不知什麼詞彙違反了當局</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542231\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw.jpg\" alt=\"CuJLo45UsAAEPBw\" width=\"450\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw.jpg 888w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw-222x300.jpg 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw-768x1038.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45UsAAEPBw-758x1024.jpg 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542234\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy.png\" alt=\"CuJLo44UkAEQA7i copy\" width=\"450\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy.png 888w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy-222x300.png 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy-768x1038.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo44UkAEQA7i-copy-758x1024.png 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/redmeteor/status/784255458735329280\" target=\"_blank\">@redmeteor</a>：是taiwan，我这本是多年前的贴条版⋯⋯</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45VYAQhA6c.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542232\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45VYAQhA6c.jpg\" alt=\"CuJLo45VYAQhA6c\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45VYAQhA6c.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45VYAQhA6c-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo45VYAQhA6c-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo43UAAAl75Z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542230\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo43UAAAl75Z.jpg\" alt=\"CuJLo43UAAAl75Z\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo43UAAAl75Z.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo43UAAAl75Z-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuJLo43UAAAl75Z-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>另：《</strong>韦氏词典》对 “<a href=\"http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/Taiwan\" target=\"_blank\">Taiwan</a>” 的解释已有更新，相比推特用户 @redmeteor 的版本，目前的更新版加入了“1895-1945 年属于日本”、台北从 1949 年后才成为中央政府所在地、地域面积等内容：</p>\n<blockquote><p>Taiwan: island China off SE coast E of Fujian; belonged to Japan 1895–1945; since 1949 seat of (Nationalist) Republic of China (∗ Taibei) area 13,807 square miles (35,760 square kilometers), pop 22,300,929</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_542240\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-542240\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾.jpg\" alt=\"韦氏台湾\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾.jpg 1510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾-300x197.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾-768x506.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/韦氏台湾-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《韦氏词典》网页截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[22646,18705,22737,8639,30520,9038]}